\end{eqnarray}
where $g_*(T_{\rm rh})$ is the number of relativisitic species in thermal bath at reheating temperature $T_{\rm rh}$, and $N_{\rm rh}$ is the number of efoldings during reheating, given by

Taking $V_{\rm end}\simeq V_*$ and choosing $g_*(T_{\rm rh})\simeq 100$ for $T_{\rm rh}\gtrsim 100\,{\rm GeV}$,  the formula for the number of efoldings becomes
\begin{eqnarray}
